{"tid":290762,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"《超級馬里奧奧德賽》有中文無韓文，韓國網友慨嘆不已","createTime":"2017-06-20T04:37:55.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-20T06:15:03.000Z","uid":22675,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"4de898ae3a5e24363973421cbf4cc97ba47bdd63","tid":290762,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-20T04:37:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://file1.a9vg.com/data/attachment/forum/201706/20/102539sn682k8kfdjau6n7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Ffile1.a9vg.com%2Fdata%2Fattachment%2Fforum%2F201706%2F20%2F102539sn682k8kfdjau6n7.jpg&h=3b9b4b30&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">曾幾何時，老任也是拿出真心對待韓國市場，不要說韓文版遊戲、連韓語配音都有</span>，廣告代言人是宋慧喬張東健，<span style=\"color: red;\">然而韓國玩家回報給老任的是破解和散裝光碟</span>。任天堂2012年因為散裝光盤問題在韓國狂賠2500多萬美元。最終任天堂大規模改組韓國分社，並將韓國從NS的首發名單中拿掉。"},{"pid":"0130cdc217ff598f271ac24718b2833453eb8fdb","tid":290762,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-20T04:42:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"502bb49a9cb9abb306f1ced293373cfef8a17e18","tid":290762,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-20T04:51:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5e581a2d1c7df5855997fee2890b063291b38a63","tid":290762,"uid":34409,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-20T05:23:05.000Z","msg":"乜野叫散裝光盤?<br />\n老任俾人破解仲要賠錢?"},{"pid":"4984f558543d9207bfcf3ddfe2c783e1516a3789","tid":290762,"uid":45213,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-20T05:24:16.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>乜野叫散裝光盤?<br />\n老任俾人破解仲要賠錢?</blockquote><br />\n應該係指蝕錢"},{"pid":"da11646213fd99f5251510ec5ef90ad6c9278059","tid":290762,"uid":89220,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-20T05:39:04.000Z","msg":"曾幾何時pokemon夠有港譯啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n係有班任豚覺得